name: Tick
description:
Inktober prompt day 14: Tick
What makes you tick? For me it's inspiration from a photo and the completion of an art piece. A great idea on a car ride. The smell of coffee. The things that keep me awake at night.
The clock face was hand drawn using micron and Pentel brush pen scanned and layered with a stock image of a bunch of watches by Heather Zabriskie and a few selfies and concert photo I took in my college days just tryin' to survive. Still am tryin'.
